libcpath
------------------------------------------
libcpath is a library for cross-platform C path functions.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.3.4-2
  libcerror1-20220101-1bl1
  libclocale1-20220107-1bl2
  libcpath-devel-20220108-1bl1
  libcpath1-20220108-1bl1
  libcsplit1-20220109-1bl1
  libuna1-20201204-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.8.0-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-1
  automake-11-1
  binutils-2.37-2
  cygport-0.34.2-1
  gcc-core-11.2.0-1
  libcerror-devel-20220101-1bl1
  libclocale-devel-20220107-1bl2
  libcsplit-devel-20220109-1bl1
  libtool-2.4.6-8
  libuna-devel-20201204-1bl1
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libyal/libcpath

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/libyal/libcpath/archive/refs/tags/20220108.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcpath-20220108-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcpath-20220108-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcpath-20220108-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcpath-20220108-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcpath1-20220108-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcpath-devel-20220108-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcpath)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcpath.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcpath/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libcpath/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libcpath/COPYING.LESSER
  /usr/share/doc/libcpath/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libcpath/README

(libcpath1)
  /usr/bin/cygcpath-1.dll

(libcpath-devel)
  /usr/include/libcpath.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/codepage.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/definitions.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/error.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/extern.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/features.h
  /usr/include/libcpath/types.h
  /usr/lib/libcpath.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libcpath.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/libcpath.3.gz

